subject: NCAA Lacrosse Championships
College Athletics
Lacrosse
lead_paragraph: Kelly McPartland scored three goals, and top-seeded Maryland defeated Northwestern, 9-6, in the semifinals of the N.C.A.A. women’s lacrosse tournament in Towson, Md.
